text: Nabiyow tawraat kitaabak ixxigâ maglab kah yontocowwime mara matablaa? Numtin-wellittee kee Yallak kalah uqbuddu haanam nummaysaanaah koroosite marak ta mari (qhureyshi koros kinnuk) yeemeneh yan marak (Nabii Mucammad ġzakfķo kee kay kataysis kinnuk) tirtô gitay massa- leh aysuk keenik Raaqan iyyan
